Description: Bindings for the 'Tabula' <http://tabula.technology/> 'Java'
    library, which can extract tables from PDF documents. The 'tabulapdfjars'
    package <https://github.com/ropensci/tabulapdfjars> provides versioned
    'Java' .jar files, including all dependencies, aligned to releases of
    'Tabula'.
